Acceptance Corp.: 8.05% 30 to 44 days; 7.75% 45 to 59 days;
7.85% 60 to 89 days; 7.80% 90 to 119 days; 7.75% 120 to 149
days; 7.70% 150 to 179 days; 7.60% 180 to 270 days.
                                                                                                       

